title: Beijing simplifies birth permit application (Beijing Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Beijing Municipal Government ) Married couples who both have Beijing household registration will be able to apply for a birth permit for their first child online by the end of 2015 , according to Beijing Municipal Commission of
